NOTE ON EXECUTABLE CODE

This repository is mostly templates and documentation, but it also ships
executable code: the hooks (hooks/*.js) and the workflows
(.claude/workflows/*.js). Those files are covered by CC BY 4.0 as well.

Creative Commons explicitly recommends against using its licenses for
software, because they do not address patent rights, source-code
availability or warranty disclaimers the way software licenses do. The
project keeps CC BY 4.0 for simplicity. The recommended direction is dual
licensing: MIT for the executable code, CC BY 4.0 for documentation and
templates.

If you need the code under an explicit software license (for example MIT
or Apache-2.0), open an issue or contact the author.
